<span class='tline' id='l7' data-llen='157:183'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0077', 'WYG', '002-1a' );" name="002-1a" class="pb">[002-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='183:191'>欽定四庫全書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='191:202'>　夏小正戴氏傳卷二</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='202:222'>　　　　　　　　　　　宋　傅崧卿　注</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='222:225'>夏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='225:248'>四月昴則見初昬南門正鳴札囿有見杏鳴蜮王萯莠</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='248:262'>取荼莠幽越有大旱執陟攻駒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='262:285'>傳四月昴則見初昬南門正南門者星也歳再見一正</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='285:308'>蓋大正所取法也鳴札札者寧縣也鳴而後知之故先</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='308:334'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0077', 'WYG', '002-1b' );" name="002-1b" class="pb">[002-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='334:357'>鳴而後札囿有見杏囿者山之燕者也鳴蜮蜮鳴也或</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='357:384'>曰屈造之屬也王萯莠取荼荼也者以為君薦蔣也<span class='krp-note'>關/本</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='384:411'><span class='krp-note'>無以/字</span>莠幽越有大旱記時爾執陟攻駒執也者始執駒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='411:440'>也<span class='krp-note'>關本作/始執駒</span>執駒也者離之去母也執而升之君也攻駒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='440:452'>也者敎之服車數舍之也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='452:481'>五月參則見浮游有殷鴂則鳴時有養日乃衣𤓰<span class='krp-note'>舊注/一作</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='481:508'><span class='krp-note'>乃衣/衣</span>良蜩鳴匽之興五日翕望乃伏啟灌藍蓼鳩為鷹</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='508:543'>唐蜩鳴初昬大火中種黍菽糜<span class='krp-note'>或曰種黍菽糜以心中/為節傳因大火中而及</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='543:569'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0077', 'WYG', '002-2a' );" name="002-2a" class="pb">[002-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='569:585'><span class='krp-note'>之非小/正文</span>煑梅蓄蘭頒馬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='585:613'>傳五月參則見參也者伐<span class='krp-note'>舊注一/作牧</span>星也故盡其辭也浮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='613:636'>游有殷殷衆也浮游殷之時也浮游者渠略也朝生而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='636:670'>暮死稱有何也有見也鴂則鳴<span class='krp-note'>大戴禮關本鴂作□/以下文考之當作鴂</span>鴂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='670:693'>者伯鷯也鳴者相命也其不辜之時也是善之故盡其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='693:716'>辭也時有養日養長也一則在本一則在末故其記曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='716:754'>時養日之也<span class='krp-note'>大戴禮日之作曰之舊/注其記曰有養日云也</span>乃衣𤓰𤓰者急𤓰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='754:794'>之辭也𤓰者始食𤓰也<span class='krp-note'>舊注一本乃衣𤓰乃衣者急/衣之辭也衣也者始創衣也</span>良</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='794:820'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0077', 'WYG', '002-2b' );" name="002-2b" class="pb">[002-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='820:843'>蜩鳴良蜩也者五采具匽之興五日翕望乃伏其不言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='843:866'>生而稱興何也不知其生之時故曰興以其興也故言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='866:889'>之興五日翕也望也者月之望也而伏云者不知其死</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='889:912'>也故謂之伏五日也者十五日也翕也者合也伏也者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='912:943'>入而不見也<span class='krp-note'>戴禮入作人/關本無也字</span>啟灌藍蓼啟者别也陶而䟽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='943:973'>之也灌也者聚生者也<span class='krp-note'>戴禮灌也/者作灌者</span>記時也鳩為鷹唐蜩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='973:996'>鳴唐蜩鳴者匽也初昬大火中大火者心也心中種黍</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='996:1033'>菽<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR1048' title='KR1048' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR1048.png'/>時也煑梅為豆實也蓄蘭為沐浴也菽<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR1048' title='KR1048' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR1048.png'/>以在纒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='1033:1059'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0077', 'WYG', '002-3a' );" name="002-3a" class="pb">[002-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='1059:1082'>經中矣又言之時何也是食短閔而記之頒馬分大夫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='1082:1114'>卿之駒也<span class='krp-note'>戴禮脫/大字</span>將閒諸則或取離駒納之則法也<span class='krp-note'>關/本</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='1114:1141'><span class='krp-note'>自是食短以下至則法也脫/簡在三月拂拂然也鳴之後</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='1141:1168'>六月初昬斗柄<span class='krp-note'>關本曰注/柄一作杓</span>正在上煑桃鷹始摯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='1168:1191'>傳六月初昬斗柄正在上五月大火中六月斗柄正在</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='1191:1214'>上此見斗柄之不在當心也蓋當依依尾也煑桃桃也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='1214:1244'>者柂桃也柂桃也者山桃也煑以為豆實也<span class='krp-note'>大戴禮拖/作柂案爾</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='1244:1291'><span class='krp-note'>雅椵柂郭璞注云白椵也樹似白楊而古今字書有杝/而無柂釋云木名亦無有訓山桃者爾雅榹桃山桃音</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='1291:1317'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0077', 'WYG', '002-3b' );" name="002-3b" class="pb">[002-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='1317:1355'><span class='krp-note'>斯唐韻亦云此書云柂桃也者/山桃也柂當作榹蓋傳寫之訛</span>鷹始摯而言之何也諱</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1355:1374'>殺之辭也故言摯云<span class='krp-note'>大戴作/故摯云</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1374:1377'>　</span><br/>
